  <div class="lcds-cta__body">
    <h2 class="lcds-cta__title">
      Learn About FDA Patient Engagement
    </h2>
    <p class="lcds-cta__text">
      Engage with FDA! Our mission is to improve public health. We can’t do it without you: the patients, caregivers, and advocates. We want to hear directly from you and learn about your experiences, preferences and needs as they relate to FDA-regulated medical products.
    </p>
    
        <a href="/patients/learn-about-fda-patient-engagement" title="/patients/learn-about-fda-patient-engagement" class="btn btn-default">
          Learn More
        </a>
    
  </div>

</section> 
</div>
          <div class="field--item">
  <section class="lcds-card-deck--teaser lcds-card-deck txt-dark">
  
                 <header class="lcds-card-deck__header">
        <h2 class="lcds-card-deck__heading">Connect with FDA</h2>
        </header>
     
  <div class="lcds-card-deck__body">
          <article class="lcds-card lcds-card--border-top lcds-card--teaser">
        <h3 class="lcds-card__title"><a href="/patients/learn-about-fda-patient-engagement/patients-ask-fda" title="Patients Ask FDA">
          Patients Ask FDA</a></h3>
        <p class="lcds-card__text">Ask a question or request a meeting with FDA.</p>
      </article>
     

          <article class="lcds-card lcds-card--border-top  lcds-card--teaser">
        <h3 class="lcds-card__title"><a href="/safety/medwatch-fda-safety-information-and-adverse-event-reporting-program" title="Report a Drug or Medical Device Issue to FDA">Report a Drug or Medical Device Issue to FDA</a></h3>
        <p class="lcds-card__text">Report a safety concern or negative event with an FDA-regulated medical product using FDA’s information and event reporting program, MedWatch.</p>
      </article>
     

          <article class="lcds-card lcds-card--border-top lcds-card--teaser">
        <h3 class="lcds-card__title"><a href="/patients/guide-submitting-comments-fda" title="Submit Comments to FDA on Pending Regulatory Policies">Submit Comments to FDA on Pending Regulatory Policies</a></h3>
        <p class="lcds-card__text">Share your knowledge and expertise with FDA to make your voice heard regarding pending regulatory policies.</p>
      </article>
     

          <article class="lcds-card lcds-card--border-top lcds-card--teaser">
        <h3 class="lcds-card__title"><a href="/about-fda/office-clinical-policy-and-programs/patient-affairs-staff" title="Contact the Patient Affairs Staff">Contact the Patient Affairs Staff</a></h3>
        <p class="lcds-card__text">Connect with FDA’s Patient Affairs Staff directly. We help patients become more informed and involved in FDA regulatory decisions related to medical products.</p>
      </article>
     

       

       

       

        

        

        

        

        

        

        

        

        
        
      
