          <div class="field--item">
  <section class="lcds-card-deck--teaser lcds-card-deck bg-light-gray txt-dark">
  
                 <header class="lcds-card-deck__header">
        <h2 class="lcds-card-deck__heading">Approval and Recalls</h2>
        </header>
     
  <div class="lcds-card-deck__body">
          <article class="lcds-card lcds-card--border-top lcds-card--teaser">
        <h3 class="lcds-card__title"><a href="/patients/learn-about-drug-and-device-approvals" title="About the FDA Drug and Device Approval Process">
          About the FDA Drug and Device Approval Process</a></h3>
        <p class="lcds-card__text">Learn about the drug and medical device approval process. This process follows well-established paths to make sure that medical products are safe and effective when they reach the public.</p>
      </article>
     

          <article class="lcds-card lcds-card--border-top  lcds-card--teaser">
        <h3 class="lcds-card__title"><a href="/drugs/development-approval-process-drugs/drug-approvals-and-databases" title="FDA Drug Approvals">FDA Drug Approvals</a></h3>
        <p class="lcds-card__text">Get information about FDA-approved brand name and generic prescription and over-the-counter human drugs and biological therapeutic products.</p>
      </article>
     

          <article class="lcds-card lcds-card--border-top lcds-card--teaser">
        <h3 class="lcds-card__title"><a href="/medical-devices/device-approvals-and-clearances/recently-approved-devices" title="FDA Device Approvals">FDA Device Approvals</a></h3>
        <p class="lcds-card__text">Find information about what the device is, how it works, when it can be used, and when it should not be used.</p>
      </article>
     

          <article class="lcds-card lcds-card--border-top lcds-card--teaser">
        <h3 class="lcds-card__title"><a href="/safety/recalls-market-withdrawals-safety-alerts" title="FDA Recalls, Market Withdrawls, &amp; Safety Alerts">FDA Recalls, Market Withdrawls, &amp; Safety Alerts</a></h3>
        <p class="lcds-card__text">Review information gathered from press releases and other public notices about recalls, withdrawls, and safety alerts of FDA-regulated products.</p>
      </article>
     

       

       

       

        

        

        

        

        

        

        

        

        
        
      
  </div>
</section>
</div>
          <div class="field--item">
  <section class="lcds-card-deck--teaser lcds-card-deck txt-dark">
  
                 <header class="lcds-card-deck__header">
        <h2 class="lcds-card-deck__heading">Expanded Access and Clinical Trials</h2>
        </header>
     
  <div class="lcds-card-deck__body">
          <article class="lcds-card lcds-card--border-top lcds-card--teaser">
        <h3 class="lcds-card__title"><a href="/news-events/expanded-access/expanded-access-information-patients" title="Expanded Access: Information for Patients">
          Expanded Access: Information for Patients</a></h3>
        <p class="lcds-card__text">Learn about expanded access, including information about the expanded access process, what FDA considers, and what costs may be involved.</p>
      </article>
     

          <article class="lcds-card lcds-card--border-top  lcds-card--teaser">
        <h3 class="lcds-card__title"><a href="/patients/learn-about-expanded-access-and-other-treatment-options" title="Learn about Expanded Access and other Treatment Options">Learn about Expanded Access and other Treatment Options</a></h3>
        <p class="lcds-card__text">Learn about treatment options for when a patient does not respond to current approved treatments.</p>
      </article>
     

          <article class="lcds-card lcds-card--border-top lcds-card--teaser">
        <h3 class="lcds-card__title"><a href="/patients/clinical-trials-what-patients-need-know" title="Clinical Trials: What Patients Need to Know">Clinical Trials: What Patients Need to Know</a></h3>
        <p class="lcds-card__text">Learn more about clinical trials and find a trial that might be right for you.</p>
      </article>
     

     

       

       

       

        

        

        

        

        

        

        

        

        
        
      
  </div>
</section>
</div>
          <div class="field--item">
  <section class="lcds-card-deck--teaser lcds-card-deck bg-light-gray txt-dark">
  
                 <header class="lcds-card-deck__header">
        <h2 class="lcds-card-deck__heading">Patient Perspectives</h2>
        </header>
     
  <div class="lcds-card-deck__body">
          <article class="lcds-card lcds-card--border-top lcds-card--teaser">
